10#ifndef HEADER_STORE_INT_H
11# define HEADER_STORE_INT_H
12
13# include <openssl/bio.h>
14# include <openssl/store.h>
15# include <openssl/ui.h>
16
17/*
18 * Two functions to read PEM data off an already opened BIO. To be used
19 * instead of OSSLSTORE_open() and OSSLSTORE_close(). Everything is done
20 * as usual with OSSLSTORE_load() and OSSLSTORE_eof().
21 */
22OSSL_STORE_CTX *ossl_store_attach_pem_bio(BIO *bp, const UI_METHOD *ui_method,
23 void *ui_data);
24int ossl_store_detach_pem_bio(OSSL_STORE_CTX *ctx);
25
26#endif
